 31 of $4.0m, up from a loss last time of $2.6m, on turnover down45.5% at $22.1m; the company simultaneously reported a net loss for the yearto September 30 of $41.5m after restructuring costs of $12.1m, up from a losslast time of $25.6m, on turnover down 16.9% at $96.1m.andP;  The figures are to UKaccounting rules.andO;</TEXT></DOC>